Package entities

Class RestaurantOrders

java.lang.Object
entities.RestaurantOrders
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class RestaurantOrders extends Object implements Serializable
The class represents an order made at a restaurant. It contains various details related to the order, such as the restaurant name, order number, total price, and other relevant information. This class implements Serializable to allow objects of this type to be serialized.
Version:
August 2024
Author:
Kfir Amoyal, Israel Ohayon, Yaniv Shatil, Noam Furman, Omri Heit, Eitan Zerbel
